<h1> OMLETTE </h1>
<p> A simple way to do delicious omlette </p>
<h2> Ingredients </h2>
<ul>
  <li> 2 Spoons of oil </li>
  <li> 4 Eggs </li>
  <li> Required amount of Salt </li>
  <li> Required amount of Pepper </li>
</ul> 
<h2> Instructions </h2>
<ol>
  <li> Add two spoons of oil to a frying pan </li>
  <li> Add some geera and some mustard </li>
  <li> Take a bowl crack the eggs and stir it very well till its mixed </li>
  <li> Now pour the egg batter in the pan </li>
  <li> Now fry the egg batter till the colour change to golden yellow </li>
  <li> Now the omlette is done change it to a bowl and enjoy your recipe </li>
</ol>
